{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>JOURNEY INTO MADNESS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Art restorer Kaelin Rykhard is invited by the reclusive painter Felix Mortimer to review his famous collection. When Rykhard arrives at the mansion, Mortimer is missing, the place is damaged, and strange artworks hint at something terrifying. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756580/extras/Gif_05_616x260.gif?t=1731876038\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>AN EVER-CHANGING\u00a0NIGHTMARE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Screams, ghouls, ghosts \u2014 make your way through an oscillating chateau ripe with\u00a0paranormal\u00a0phenomena never repeating and always spine-chilling. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756580/extras/Gif_02_O1_616x260.gif?t=1731876038\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>GAME FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Voice the monster using your microphone;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Record a message into your microphone and listen to it on the in-game Gordon Baker Radio Show, it should be fun;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Each location has unique mechanics, so you will need to find the right ways to survive;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> The environment is fully interactive and has many details to explore.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756580/extras/Gif_03_O1_616x260.gif?t=1731876038\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2756580/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731876038","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/ste